name: Oscillation to the Edge by Maria Finkelmeier

metadata.name: Into Eternity 1/2
metadata.description: Into Eternity is a rich discovery of hues and depth, as we leap into unknown moments that transform our basic understanding of how and what we hear. As we reflect upon our concept of eternity, how do we listen, create stillness, and let the sonic world envelop us?
